title: Proxy Switcher Pro_5.19.0 Build 7358
description:
Proxy Switcher





Proxy Switcher: is an easy-to-use proxy settings management software that provides flexible proxy server list,
and anonymous surfing capabilities. With Proxy Switcher you will be easily to unblock
and access websites blocked by your ISP, accelerate upstream and downstream speeds,
hide your real IP address and surf anonymously.
You can select and specify a proxy you want to use,
each proxy has its own strengths and weaknesses,
select and use the highest possible.
The software provides proxy management,
automatic proxy switching, proxy server finder,
proxy server tester and anonymous proxy server list downloader.




Key features:


1-Access to various website anonymously
2-Anonymous proxy server downloader
3-Automatic proxy switching capability
4-Avoid all sorts of limitations sites
5-Change the proxy much faster and easier
6-Control proxy scanner and downloader
7-Full featured connection management
8-Manually change the proxy settings
9-Proxy tester, and custom proxy server
10-And many more
